## Background
Foundation cho 13 dialect. Mỗi dialect là 1 implementation trait `Dialect` với InbandScanner parse XML tags từ streaming text.

## What to build
File: `crates/jcode-llm-dialects/src/lib.rs`

Define:
```rust
pub enum DialectId { Anthropic, Deepseek, Gemini, Gemma, Glm, Harmony, Hermes, Kimi, Minimax, Pi, Qwen3, Xml, Jcode }

pub trait Dialect: Send + Sync {
    fn id(&self) -> DialectId;
    fn create_scanner(&self) -> Box<dyn InbandScanner>;
    fn render_tool_call(&self, call: &ToolCall) -> String;
    fn render_assistant_tool_calls(&self, calls: &[ToolCall]) -> String;
    fn render_tool_results(&self, results: &[ToolResult]) -> String;
    fn render_thinking(&self, thinking: &str) -> String;
}

pub trait InbandScanner: Send {
    fn feed(&mut self, text: &str) -> Vec<InbandScanEvent>;
    fn finish(&mut self) -> Vec<InbandScanEvent>;
}

pub enum InbandScanEvent {
    ToolCallStart { id: String, name: String },
    ToolCallDelta { id: String, delta: String },
    ToolCallEnd { id: String, name: String, input: serde_json::Value },
    ThinkingDelta { delta: String },
}

pub static DIALECT_REGISTRY: LazyLock<HashMap<DialectId, Arc<dyn Dialect>>> = ...;

pub fn preferred_dialect(model_id: &str) -> DialectId { /* map model id to dialect */ }
```

`preferred_dialect` logic:
- `claude-*` → Anthropic
- `minimax-*` → Minimax
- `kimi-*`, `moonshot-*` → Kimi
- `qwen*` → Qwen3
- `deepseek-*` → Deepseek
- `glm-*` → Glm
- `gemini-*` (in some cases) → Gemini
- `gemma-*` → Gemma
- `gpt-oss-*`, `*-harmony` → Harmony
- `*-hermes` → Hermes
- unknown → Xml (fallback)

