## Background
Wire failover walker vào `stream_completion`. Trên first error retryable, walk sang entry tiếp theo trong chain.

## What to build
File: `crates/jcode-provider-app/src/stream_completion.rs` (NEW)

```rust
pub async fn stream_completion(
    request: LlmRequest,
    catalog: &Catalog,
    integration: &Integration,
    chain: &FailoverChain,
    policy: &FailoverPolicy,
    vcr: &VcrRecorder,
) -> Result<Pin<Box<dyn Stream<Item = LlmEvent> + Send>>, LlmError> {
    for attempt in 0..policy.max_attempts {
        let current = if attempt == 0 {
            request.model.clone()
        } else {
            match next_entry(chain, current, last_error.unwrap(), policy) {
                Some(m) => m,
                None => break,
            }
        };
        match try_stream(current, request, integration, vcr).await {
            Ok(stream) => return Ok(stream),
            Err(e) => {
                let class = classify(&e);
                if !policy.retryable_errors.contains(&class) {
                    return Err(e);
                }
                last_error = Some(e);
                // Cooldown check
                if is_in_cooldown(current) {
                    continue;
                }
                set_cooldown(current);
                log_failover(current, e);
            }
        }
    }
    Err(last_error.unwrap())
}
```

Cooldown state: in-memory `Arc<Mutex<HashMap<ModelRef, Instant>>>` (Phase 7.5 sẽ persist).

